Name: Riedell  Hockey Set - Bruin
Description: Classic design meets modern performance in the Bruin recreational hockey skate from Riedell.  Durable polyester mesh uppers designed with a timeless hockey look are backed with high density foam and brushed nylon linings that will have you feeling as good as you look, whether you’re out for a casual date skate or playing a pick-up game on the pond with your friends.  To give the Bruin the lasting performance you need, the tongues incorporate a supportive EVA foam pad for protection against lace bite, and every pair is fitted with reinforced nylon outsoles, blade holders, and toe caps that have been tested to withstand high impact events should you find yourself in the way of an oncoming slap shot.  With comfort where you want it and strength where you need it, the Bruin welcomes you to get out onto the ice time and time again.

Name: Rollerblade Micro Ice G, Adjustable Ice Skates
Description: Micro Ice skates take a lot of the frustration out of the ice skating experience for parents and kids alike. The Micro Ice is a 4 size adjustable skate with an easy to use push-button system allowing it to grow with the child's feet. It is a great value product kids can use for multiple years that parents can also share with younger siblings when the child grows out of them. Micro Ice skates are comfortable the moment kids put them on because of the well padded liner and supportive structure. These convenient skates are an ideal option from renting skates and provide a positive and enjoyable experience on the ice. Kids of all skating levels and abilities will benefit from the support, comfort and value of the Micro Ice.

Name: Riedell  Ruby Ice Skates (Width D)
Description: The Riedell Ruby features synthetic reinforcements and light support for enjoyment on the ice. This skate set also offers a modern ergonomic toe fit for out-of-the-box comfort. The plush hand rolled collar provides relief to the Achilles tendon and a flex notch design facilitates proper knee and ankle bend. Beyond the technical features, each skate is adorned with faux crystals in the backstay and a decorative gem lace bar for added sparkle on the ice.

Name: Riedell  Figure Skating Set - Sparkle (Ice Blue)
Description: The Riedell Sparkle is perfect for the recreational or beginning skater, with the comfort and performance you need to make memories on the ice. From the moment you first slip them on, the soft, padded lining, stabilizing split tongue design, and reinforced lace hooks all work in unison to keep your feet comfortable and secure. No detail on the Sparkle was overlooked, with sparkling glitter accents adding a stylish look to the durable, 100% vegan uppers that protect your feet from the ice and cold, and no maintenance PVC soles and stainless steel blades providing a hassle-free experience from the start to the end of your skating season. Featuring a chic look and proper support where you want it, let the Sparkle be your guide to all the ice has to offer!

Rollerblade Micro Ice G, Adjustable Ice Skates
Description: Micro Ice skates take a lot of the frustration out of the ice skating experience for parents and kids alike. The Micro Ice is a 4 size adjustable skate with an easy to use push-button system allowing it to grow with the child's feet. It is a great value product kids can use for multiple years that parents can also share with younger siblings when the child grows out of them. Micro Ice skates are comfortable the moment kids put them on because of the well padded liner and supportive structure. These convenient skates are an ideal option from renting skates and provide a positive and enjoyable experience on the ice. Kids of all skating levels and abilities will benefit from the support, comfort and value of the Micro Ice.

Name: Riedell  Topaz Ice Skates (Width D)
Description: The Riedell Topaz is ideal for skaters in group classes and is available in both black and white. With a performance microfiber upper and a moderate level of support, Topaz is a great choice for skaters looking to master their skills whether they are a beginner or starting single jumps.

Name: Riedell  Ruby Ice Skates (Width D)
Description: The Riedell Ruby features synthetic reinforcements and light support for enjoyment on the ice. This skate set also offers a modern ergonomic toe fit for out-of-the-box comfort. The plush hand rolled collar provides relief to the Achilles tendon and a flex notch design facilitates proper knee and ankle bend. Beyond the technical features, each skate is adorned with faux crystals in the backstay and a decorative gem lace bar for added sparkle on the ice.

Name: Riedell  Crystal Ice Skates
Description: With the Eclipse Vesta blade and supportive reinforced uppers, theRiedell Crystalhelps skaters shine as they work on single jumps and land that first Axel. Crystal is also an ideal choice for adults looking to skate for fun and fitness, or any recreational skater wanting high-quality equipment.

Name: Riedell Horizon Ice Skates (Medium width)
Description: Horizon is built with a modern ergonomic toe fit for out-of-the-box comfort. The soft liner, rolled collar, and supportive cushion ensure a comfortable and positive skating experience for all. Synthetic uppers provide durability as well as light support, while the split tongue design offers stability on the ice. In addition, a stainless steel blade provides smooth edges for gliding across the ice.
